comment: Young (BKN) establishes legal guarding position prior to the contact by Morris (PHX).
Lopez (BKN) sets the screen on Tucker (PHX) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Bledsoe (PHX) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Larkin's (BKN) drive.
Lopez (BKN) remains vertical as he defends Bledsoe's (PHX) layup attempt. Any contact on the play is initiated by Bledsoe.
Lopez (BKN) makes incidental contact with Bledsoe (PHX) after setting the screen.
Young (BKN) maintains legal guarding position as Len (PHX) attempts a layup.
Hollis-Jefferson (BKN) makes incidental contact with Teletovic (PHX) prior to the inbounds that does not affect his ability to catch the pass.
Jack (BKN) cleanly blocks Knight's (PHX) shot attempt.
